    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太空工程师》“接触包”包含加特林和火箭炮塔变体、方形活塞变体、抛物面天线变体、小型门、模块化桥梁套件、泛光灯套件、厨房套件、模块化货箱、队长的桌子、急救箱、床铺和媒体播放器。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加特林炮塔 II 型（1 个方块，大型 + 小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种加特林炮塔的全新视觉风格受到了现实世界军事武器的启发。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/e4c5950e1988f19bb216497d6d50f678.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/e4c5950e1988f19bb216497d6d50f678.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/e4c5950e1988f19bb216497d6d50f678.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >火箭炮塔 II 型（1 个方块，大型 + 小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火箭炮塔的高科技军事重新设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/f2c4ba9164bba3c5f1ee8818c5136ebf.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/f2c4ba9164bba3c5f1ee8818c5136ebf.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/f2c4ba9164bba3c5f1ee8818c5136ebf.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小型高门（1 个方块，大型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >垂直打开的大型门道。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9eec5bdba43b29f034d1e27cc77461e1.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9eec5bdba43b29f034d1e27cc77461e1.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9eec5bdba43b29f034d1e27cc77461e1.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小型宽门（1 个方块，大型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水平打开的大型门道。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/c0fc217c9487ef40ae5c9a9a46173a73.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/c0fc217c9487ef40ae5c9a9a46173a73.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/c0fc217c9487ef40ae5c9a9a46173a73.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模块化桥梁套件（11 个方块，大型网格） </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一套具有加固窗户和控制方块的方块，可以组合构成适合大型网格飞船的完美桥梁。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/50013e43d535801f4c3ac99011e845a0.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/50013e43d535801f4c3ac99011e845a0.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/50013e43d535801f4c3ac99011e845a0.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >队长的桌子（1 个方块，大型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个适合坚忍领导者的工作站！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/32300b7ebaff9058527e233e663e82dd.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/32300b7ebaff9058527e233e663e82dd.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/32300b7ebaff9058527e233e663e82dd.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >方形活塞（1 个方块，大型 + 小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种采用坚固工业美学设计的活塞方块。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/da040e3333928ab443562380b9ac3d70.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/da040e3333928ab443562380b9ac3d70.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/da040e3333928ab443562380b9ac3d70.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >泛光灯套件（4 个方块，大型网格 + 6 个方块，小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一套能够以多种角度放置的聚光灯。 非常适合照亮任何工作空间，或者保持周边安全。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9112eb93e8eb6c104938e5108dcd1aa4.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9112eb93e8eb6c104938e5108dcd1aa4.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/9112eb93e8eb6c104938e5108dcd1aa4.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抛物面天线（1 个方块，大型 + 小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种类似于现代雷达天线的紧凑型天线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/03d6a35beac41b4d884dff39ed889516.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/03d6a35beac41b4d884dff39ed889516.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/03d6a35beac41b4d884dff39ed889516.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >厨房套件（5 个方块，小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一套模块化厨房方块，是在小型网格内增加生活空间的完美选择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/ca93570e3f593ac022523a0329338745.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/ca93570e3f593ac022523a0329338745.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/ca93570e3f593ac022523a0329338745.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >急救箱（1 个方块，小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个用于存放医疗包和设备的储物柜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/29f10076fd3e95912d405c4c1205c4bc.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/29f10076fd3e95912d405c4c1205c4bc.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/29f10076fd3e95912d405c4c1205c4bc.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >床铺（1 个方块，小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个适合小型网格的紧凑型睡眠空间。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/487c96d3661a4a90a831e7fa118311e2.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/487c96d3661a4a90a831e7fa118311e2.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/487c96d3661a4a90a831e7fa118311e2.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模块化货箱（1 个方块，大型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种货箱变体能够在易于堆叠的模块化框架内储存适量货物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/fd474d86918c7a26031dd2e4bd6099f9.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/fd474d86918c7a26031dd2e4bd6099f9.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/fd474d86918c7a26031dd2e4bd6099f9.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >媒体播放器（1 个方块，小型网格）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一块配备扬声器系统的时尚平板屏幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/1232ef6a0122bae2439c00d2bf73ceb7.poster.avif?t=1739191808\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/1232ef6a0122bae2439c00d2bf73ceb7.webm?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066290/extras/1232ef6a0122bae2439c00d2bf73ceb7.mp4?t=1739191808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
